-- Migration 43: Add missing indexes on FK columns
-- Phát hiện: Sprint 1 P1.6 R23 CHECK 02 — 416 FK columns thiếu index
-- Pattern: CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY IF NOT EXISTS (production-grade, idempotent)
-- Created: 2026-05-15 (Sprint 2 Day 2)
-- Refactored: 2026-05-15 (switch from BEGIN/COMMIT regular → CONCURRENTLY)
--
-- NOTE: KHÔNG có BEGIN/COMMIT vì CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY
-- không cho phép chạy trong transaction.
-- Mỗi statement là 1 transaction riêng (autocommit).
-- Nếu apply fail giữa chừng:
--   - IF NOT EXISTS đảm bảo re-run idempotent
--   - Check INVALID indexes: SELECT WHERE NOT indisvalid
--   - Cleanup: DROP INDEX <invalid_index>; rồi re-apply
--
-- Apply command:
--   psql -U postgres -d medusa --set ON_ERROR_STOP=off -f 43_fk_indexes.sql
--

